00:39:45,562 --> 00:39:47,976
They normally don't even retire.
Just wave it through.

551
00:39:48,064 --> 00:39:49,474
Listen, is Halliwell's daughter

552
00:39:49,561 --> 00:39:52,361
still up for us taping them
