631
00:44:58,561 --> 00:45:00,212
I know why you're here.

632
00:45:00,440 --> 00:45:02,240
Mrs Edwards, can I come in?

633
00:45:02,580 --> 00:45:03,900
Oh, my God...!

634
00:45:04,326 --> 00:45:07,900
It's my daughter, isn't it?
