Sorry, yes, I am.

640
00:45:21,906 --> 00:45:23,256
- No! My God!
- Mum?

641
00:45:23,344 --> 00:45:24,474
- Mum?
- Karen!

642
00:45:24,667 --> 00:45:25,706
Steve!

643
00:45:25,856 --> 00:45:27,125
Karen...

644
00:45:29,193 --> 00:45:31,778
It's all right, Mum.
